{"tid":1079824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完急症 男友都唔黎陪我","createTime":"2019-03-27T07:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T09:17:09.000Z","uid":132281,"like":26,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"149acfb1ffc27b3d3e9705046fb80d7da7b43a1d","tid":1079824,"uid":132281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"今朝因為啲事去咗睇急症，<br />\n話嚴重又唔係好嚴重，<br />\n但係都要轉介去覆診再做檢查。<br />\n睇完叫男朋友黎我度陪我，<br />\n佢就話我病，要休息，但係我個病唔係會令人攰嗰種，<br />\n我就話佢唔陪我，<br />\n佢就話我病，黎我度淨係陪我瞓覺😐<br />\n跟住我話我都唔眼瞓，佢就話咁黎又有咩做，<br />\n完全好似唔想陪我咁，加上佢依排其實冇野做，唔洗返工。<br />\n咁我咪話算啦，你唔好黎啦，之後佢打黎我語氣都唔係咁好。<br />\n我後尾開門見山話佢嗰陣，佢就話咩唔想黎到瞓覺又冇野做，又話之後打返俾我問我，我又講晦氣說話，話唔想估我諗咩。<br />\n<br />\n到底係我定我男朋友問題？<br />\n<br />\n男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a480e495952eec1e5fe4e8390bc70b03aab09ae","tid":1079824,"uid":17019,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"我黎陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317677d4ccc0dc7a3f4ab75b534a846e9695500e","tid":1079824,"uid":132227,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"連男友都唔想同你扑嘢 你究竟幾撚豬？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb196ab220b4b5d5ec708223978cfbeafb5671e","tid":1079824,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ca1961168fc0b496a0188115b635b41e91f0520","tid":1079824,"uid":123848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"濫用急症室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb7eb4394335b890266620297630e47c13fa05f","tid":1079824,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"你唔訓人地都